Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 1 January 2019. Two images: (1) Angel figure with wings holding roses, 'Happy New Year' text, (2) Colorful heart painting with light emerging from the centre — rainbow energies swirling around a golden light at the heart's core. Divine feminine angel + heart chakra activation imagery. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Shakti — feminine divine energy and heart chakra as the path of transformation.
